Company Description


Taptica International Ltd. offers online advertising solutions to advertisers and publishers worldwide. The company provides managed services for large and medium sized publishers, as well as self serve products for smaller publishers, such as blogs and small business Websites. Taptica International was founded by Maia Shiran and Ariel Cababie on March 20, 2007 and is headquartered in Tel Aviv, Israel.




